State in compliance with victim rights legislation.  The Court orders restitution in the stipulated amount of $1895.00 payable to Rodney U.- bail to apply from this case and 14CF1325.  Defense requests restitution hearing as to disputed amount.  The Court orders the balance of bail held pending restitution hearing.  The Court ordered that all financial obligations and restitution be paid through collection of sums by the Department of Corrections from 25% of funds under Sec. 973.05(4)(b) and as a condition of extended supervision.  Any amount remaining due and owing is subject to civil judgment.  Pursuant to Wisconsin Statutes Section 973.176, the Court advised the defendant of the following restrictions:  Firearm possession and Voting.
